{"lemma":"غالِ","slug":"غالِ","root":"NTWS","root_slug":"NTWS","root_link":"/words/roots/NTWS","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32177","n32331"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"expensive (having a high price), dear, costly, precious"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"boiling, seething"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"extremist, fanatic, zealot"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Gauls","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"ومن الحوادث التاريخية المهمة هو انهُ انتشب القتال بين ماريوس قنصل رومة وبين امبرونس وتوتونس في بلاد الغال فقتل من الغال ٢٩٠ الف نفر"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of غَلَا (ḡalā, “to be excessive, to be or become expensive”).\n\nBorrowed from Latin Gallus."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32177","headword_ar":"غَالٌّ","root":"gl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; and its fem., with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed, ground, in which are trees, and places of growth of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the trees called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"salam","text_ar":"سَلَم"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloH","text_ar":"طَلْح"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAl~N","text_ar":"غَالٌّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino salamK","text_ar":"مِنْ سَلَمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiyoSN mino sidorK","text_ar":"عِيْصٌ مِنْ سِدْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiymapN mino gaDFA","text_ar":"قَصِيمَةٌ مِنْ غَضًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AHn, S, O:) or, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galiylN","text_ar":"غَلِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place of growth of"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the trees called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaloH","text_ar":"طَلْح"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed, valley"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"torrent-bed in the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which are trees:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~aAnN","text_ar":"غُلَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain plant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K,) [said to be]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K: [but I have not found it to be now known:]) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~aAnN","text_ar":"غُلَّانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["AHn","S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n32331","headword_ar":"غَالٍ","root":"glw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[act. part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galaA","text_ar":"غَلَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": and hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Acting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaving, with forced hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strictness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rigour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in religion,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that he exceeds the proper, due,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"common, limit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1:) and particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an extravagant zealot of the class of innovators:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gulaApN","text_ar":"غُلَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sbA^","text_ar":"سبا"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Shooting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who shoots, the arrow to the furthest distance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"High,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excessive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, K, TA,) applied to a price, or rate, at which a thing is sold; (S, Msb, K, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galiY~N","text_ar":"غَلِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) Hence one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEotuhu biAlgaAliY","text_ar":"بِعْتُهُ بِالغَالِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlgaliY~i","text_ar":"بِالغَلِىِّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sold it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bought it, at what was a high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an excessive, price,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rate."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) A poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"walawo A^an~aA nubaAEa kalaAma salomaY\n                      \n                     ↓ \n      laA^aEoTayonaA bihi vamanFA galiy~aA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And if we were sold the speech,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discourse, of Selmà, we would give for it a high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an excessive, price"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat flesh-meat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}